## PatternFly Era Reference

| Era | Versions | PF Class Prefix |
|-----|----------|-----------------|
| Legacy | 4.12–4.14 | `.pf-c-*` |
| PF5 | 4.15–4.18 | `.pf-v5-c-*` |
| PF6 | 4.19–4.21 | `.pf-v6-c-*` |

PF class selectors in the spec files target the release's UI and should be preserved unless the live cluster shows they have changed. `data-test-id` / `data-test` selectors are PF-era-agnostic and preferred where available.

